498
00:19:03.745 --> 00:19:06.781
Cool bubble. You need
help marketing that?

499
00:19:06.814 --> 00:19:08.482
Only if you
put Jerry on it.

500
00:19:08.516 --> 00:19:09.717
Uh. done.

501
00:19:09.751 --> 00:19:11.184
[ Groans ]

502
00:19:11.218 --> 00:19:13.121
Oh. just make sure
there's enough of him

503
00:19:13.186 --> 00:19:15.056
to go around. huh?
[ Laughs ]

504
00:19:15.089 --> 00:19:17.825
Jerry. you start
on Monday.

505
00:19:17.859 --> 00:19:19.393
Congrats. hon!

506
00:19:19.426 --> 00:19:21.428
[ Groans ]

507
00:19:23.163 --> 00:19:25.733
Sweet Marie
would have loved this.

508
00:19:25.767 --> 00:19:27.200
Who?

509
00:19:27.234 --> 00:19:30.270
[ Rumbling ]

510
00:19:31.639 --> 00:19:34.341
Is there something
wrong with dogs?

511
00:19:34.374 --> 00:19:37.045
I was just trying
to be like you.

512
00:19:37.078 --> 00:19:39.080
I'm so ashamed.
Morty.

513
00:19:39.113 --> 00:19:40.414
Oh. Snowball!

514
00:19:40.447 --> 00:19:42.917
Humans are ashamed
all the time.

515
00:19:42.950 --> 00:19:44.585
You guys
used to be wolves.

516
00:19:44.619 --> 00:19:47.354
Humans. we -- we used
to be sub-hyena.

517
00:19:47.387 --> 00:19:50.058
I think we invented shame
and judgment to cope.

518
00:19:50.091 --> 00:19:52.225
I suppose no creature
is perfect.

519
00:19:52.259 --> 00:19:54.629
Yeah. if we put giraffes
in charge.

520
00:19:54.662 --> 00:19:57.632
they'd just invent. you know.
neck racism. probably.

521
00:19:57.665 --> 00:20:00.635
[ Chuckles ] They <i>do</i> have
those necks. don't they?

522
00:20:00.668 --> 00:20:02.369
Haha. Yeah.

523
00:20:02.402 --> 00:20:06.607
Maybe our species can be
self-conscious together.

524
00:20:09.476 --> 00:20:10.477
[ Beep ]

525
00:20:12.947 --> 00:20:14.615
[ Dog barking ]

526
00:20:15.650 --> 00:20:17.417
Snowball:
Rick? I can explain.

527
00:20:17.451 --> 00:20:19.419
-Easy. buddy.
-Whoa. What happened here?

528
00:20:19.453 --> 00:20:21.122
Four days of civil war.

529
00:20:21.155 --> 00:20:22.456
I never took
a moral stance.

530
00:20:22.489 --> 00:20:24.324
though I resisted
at every turn.

531
00:20:24.357 --> 00:20:26.359
Y-Y-You would have been
so proud of me!
Really?

532
00:20:26.393 --> 00:20:29.664
Couldn't pin me down to
nothing. Totally sidelined it.

533
00:20:29.697 --> 00:20:31.632
Hahaha! Good boy.

534
00:20:33.634 --> 00:20:36.336
So. should we just leave it
like this. then. or...?

535
00:20:36.369 --> 00:20:37.805
I feel bad
for Snowball.

536
00:20:37.839 --> 00:20:40.373
He -- He built a monorail.
and now it's all blown up.

537
00:20:40.407 --> 00:20:42.744
a-and everyone's dying.

538
00:20:45.046 --> 00:20:46.581
Well...

539
00:20:50.450 --> 00:20:52.086
Dogs and worms. baby.

540
00:20:52.120 --> 00:20:55.156
I guess every conflict can
be solved with free narcotics.

541
00:20:55.189 --> 00:20:56.423
What a lesson.

542
00:20:56.456 --> 00:20:58.159
Oh. hey.
What happened with Dad?

543
00:20:58.192 --> 00:21:00.161
Did -- Did he
get that job?

544
00:21:00.194 --> 00:21:01.996
[Burps] Advertising
people are perverts.

545
00:21:02.029 --> 00:21:03.564
So no?
Yes.

546
00:21:03.598 --> 00:21:04.632
Alright!

547
00:21:04.665 --> 00:21:12.840
♪♪

548
00:21:12.874 --> 00:21:22.049
♪♪

549
00:21:22.083 --> 00:21:28.823
♪♪

550
00:21:28.856 --> 00:21:33.694
♪♪

551
00:21:37.632 --> 00:21:39.901
So it's all hands
on deck this week.

552
00:21:39.934 --> 00:21:42.870
Jerry! We're throwing darts
at the interns!

553
00:21:42.904 --> 00:21:45.139
Get in here!
Yes. sir!

554
00:21:45.173 --> 00:21:48.209
Boy. I really set
a weird bar for myself.

555
00:21:48.242 --> 00:21:49.744
Sorry. I gotta
wrap this up.

556
00:21:49.777 --> 00:21:52.713
But I wish every client
was as chill as you guys.

557
00:21:52.747 --> 00:21:54.582
I <i>love</i> working
on this account.

558
00:21:54.615 --> 00:21:56.717
Ad dog:
<i>You're the man. Jerry.</i>

559
00:21:56.751 --> 00:22:00.420
<i>-This guy. Sell anything.</i>
-Glug! Ug!

560
00:22:02.023 --> 00:22:03.591
<i>Did you get any of that?</i>

